391
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,040
Doggo.

392
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,040
What's wrong with you?

393
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:18,080
Share your sad story with us.

394
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:19,600
Let's share it.

395
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,320
Anran said

396
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:24,920
I am just a good friend to her.

397
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:31,640
What?

398
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,680
I don't understand, Doggo.

399
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,560
I'm sure it's hard to understand, Teaty.

400
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:37,320
This is so subtle.

401
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:45,000
Don't be sad, Doggo.

402
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:47,000
Don't be sad, Teaty.

403
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,720
Your father will get better.

404
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:57,560
You and Anran will become best friends

405
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,880
from good friend.

406
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:05,960
What the heck, Teaty?

407
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,240
Save a set for me, OK?

408
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,080
Get it.

409
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:24,480
Do you still drive during the Spring Festival?

410
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,240
Yes, just one more day.

411
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,240
Drive safe.

412
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:26,880
OK.

413
00:23:28,280 --> 00:23:29,440
Luo Shenxi.

414
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:31,880
What? Come on.

415
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:35,640
Come on! You lazy.

416
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,200
What are you doing?

417
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:01,440
You're awake.

418
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:02,160
I'll make you some hot dishes.

419
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,000
Don't touch my things.

420
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,520
That apron was my mom's.

421
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:19,840
Why are you still here?

422
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:21,880
I...

423
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:22,920
I am waiting for your dad.

424
00:24:23,360 --> 00:24:24,000
It's getting dark.

425
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,720
Wait for what?

426
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:30,280
Dishes are ready.

427
00:24:32,160 --> 00:24:33,520
Enjoy yourselves.

428
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,640
Where is your Aunt Zhang?

429
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:46,680
Didn't she promise to cook dinner on Chinese New Year's Eve?

430
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,680
I don't know. Maybe she left.

431
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,000
What do you mean?

432
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,400
Uncle, do you feel better?

433
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,560
I am OK.

434
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:04,440
Don't worry about me.

435
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:06,600
You rest assured.

436
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:08,560
I am just getting old.

437
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:10,640
It's OK for you to get old.

438
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,160
Teaty is such an adult.

439
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:14,480
And you two are with each other.

440
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:16,160
It's not like my mother.

441
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:17,400
For so many years,

442
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,760
she has been taking care of the family alone?

443
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:21,080
I hope she finds someone to accompany her.

444
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,560
Hey, you guys

445
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:23,840
are growing up

446
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,600
while we are growing old.

447
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,960
But it's good to have a partner when you are old.

448
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:34,480
Partner.

449
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:39,280
Big Mouth,

450
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:45,760
if your mother suddenly

451
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:47,080
brings a boyfriend, what will you do?

452
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,640
It will be hard for me to get used to it.

453
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:53,440
Me, either.

454
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:55,280
But I will feel happy for her.

455
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:58,720
Because after so many years,

456
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:00,520
she finally finds someone to stay with her.

457
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,200
Isn't that a good thing?

458
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,800
Yes.

459
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:10,160
Just asking. Come on.

460
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:11,480
I won't drive for money today.

461
00:27:12,600 --> 00:27:14,040
Let's buy new year goods.

462
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,480
Mom.

463
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:18,680
I wanted to visit Coco in Wanzhou before the new year.

464
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,720
Why?

465
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,880
Mom, I'll come back the day I leave.

466
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,240
Sorry for keeping you waiting so long.

467
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:31,320
This is your Aunt Chen.

468
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,100
Hello, Aunt Chen.

469
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,360
A lift to Luohan Temple?

470
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:37,880
No meter ten yuan, OK?

471
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:38,600
Good.

472
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:42,260
Jia,

473
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:43,840
ask him.

474
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,960
Ask what?

475
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:46,280
Him!

476
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,560
Did you give up?

477
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,440
Once you were interviewed for this.

478
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,440
You!

479
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,680
Don'y say that now.

480
00:28:01,080 --> 00:28:02,120
It is said that in Yuzhong District

481
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,560
there is one female taxi driver.

482
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:04,920
Every time a passenger gets in her car,

483
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:07,120
she would ask the passengers with a photo

484
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,640
about the information of her missing husband?

485
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:10,080
She was right behind us today.

486
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:11,720
What kind of story does she have?

487
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:12,920
Let's find out.

488
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:14,800
Lady Zhang

489
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:16,160
is that taxi driver.

490
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:16,920
Hello, Ms. Zhang

491
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:17,640
Kid.

492
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:19,560
Have some fruit.

493
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,880
Mom, leave this fruit on the table.

494
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,040
What?

495
00:28:24,280 --> 00:28:25,960
What's wrong with you?

496
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:27,120
Mom.

497
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,480
Get out. I'm going to change my clothes.

498
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:29,520
I'm not going out.

499
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:31,160
Don't turn it off.

500
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,880
Why can I hear my own speech?

501
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:36,400
I used to do business with my husband.

502
00:28:36,600 --> 00:28:37,280
We were bankrupt

503
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:38,800
and owed a lot of money.

504
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,320
Afterwards,

505
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:42,320
a friend told us that

506
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:44,840
working on ships get get easy money.

507
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,880
He went with his friends.

508
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,520
He had been away for several years.

509
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,160
Then he went missing.

510
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:55,000
I have thought about all the possible results.

511
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,720
But I can't give up.

512
00:28:58,160 --> 00:29:00,480
I put his photo on the taxi.

513
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:01,680
I ask about him when I meet someone.

514
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:04,440
People think I'm stupid. They laugh at me.

515
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:05,400
But I think

516
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,240
every silver lining

517
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,800
counts.

518
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:11,880
Have you been working hard alone these years?

519
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:14,520
I can handle that.

520
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,720
Driving a taxi

521
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,080
while raising the child

522
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:20,280
is not easy.

523
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:23,080
But seeing my child grow up day by day

524
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:24,960
and thinking that in the future

525
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:26,200
he may go to college

526
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:27,560
and have his own family,

527
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,280
I still feel very happy.

528
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,280
I think everything

529
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:32,440
is worthy.

530
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:46,920
Dad, you are awake.

531
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,800
Who are you?

532
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,720
I just found out today that

533
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,840
you and mother are old.

534
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:04,560
Right.

535
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:08,080
There is a box in that cabinet.

536
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:09,760
Take it out.

537
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:12,440
OK.

538
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,400
This.

539
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:23,320
Open it.

540
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:37,200
PROPERTY OWNERSHIP CERTIFICATE
LIFE INSURANCE CONTRACT

541
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,520
What does this mean?

542
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,040
I can't understand it.

543
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:52,720
The year when your mom was pregnant with you

544
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:55,640
we were hesitant about the future.

545
00:30:56,360 --> 00:30:58,240
Because we were different from others.

546
00:30:58,880 --> 00:30:59,520
First,

547
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:02,640
your mother is a super-old pregnant woman.

548
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,520
It can be very dangerous.

549
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:07,920
Second,

550
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:11,000
we are aware that

551
00:31:12,560 --> 00:31:13,880
when you haven't grown up yet

552
00:31:15,520 --> 00:31:16,440
we'll be old.

553
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:20,200
But we decided to give birth to you.

554
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,080
So all these years

555
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:25,720
we made some preparations in advance.

556
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:29,440
Because

557
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,360
we don't know for how long we can take care of you.

558
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:05,280
AGRICULTURAL BANK OF CHINA
UNIVERSITY TUITION PASSWORD: 205748

559
00:32:05,280 --> 00:32:08,800
FOR MARRIAGE PASSWORD: 047015

560
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:22,840
FOR THE BIRTH OF YOUR KID PASSWORD: 555122

561
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,760
IN CASE YOU HAVE TWO BABIES PASSWORD: 203100

562
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,880
Liangliang,

563
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:32,800
you must accept this.

564
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:35,680
(EMERGENCY PASSWORD: 312822)
And,

565
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,360
(IF YOU WANT A CAR PASSWORD: 651614)
from today,

566
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:40,800
and every day after that,

567
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:45,000
prepare yourself for that.

568
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,600
I didn't ask what you can do for me.

569
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,080
I just hope you

570
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,720
grow up happily and safely.

571
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,640
Then find another person who can accompany you.

572
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:04,920
If you can do these,

573
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:11,720
no matter when your mom and I leave,

574
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,600
we will not have any

575
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:16,600
regret.

576
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,920
Why turn off the light?

577
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:05,880
Why do you always

578
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,960
sleep with the light on?

579
00:34:08,080 --> 00:34:09,000
Mind your own business.

580
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,480
Do you think

581
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:14,400
it is a little lonely at home?

582
